Package org.neo4j.internal.batchimport.cache.idmapping.string

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CollisionValues
    Stores collision values efficiently for retrieval later.
    Encoder
    Encodes a Object into a long.
    EncodingIdMapper.Monitor  
    GroupCache
    Cache for keeping nodeId --> groupId mapping.
    ParallelSort.Comparator
    Pluggable comparator for the comparisons that quick-sort needs in order to function.
    Tracker
    EncodingIdMapper is an index where arbitrary ids, be it String or long or whatever can be added and mapped to an internal (node) long id.
    TrackerFactory
    Factory for Tracker instances.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractTracker<ARRAY extends NumberArray>
    Base implementation of Tracker over a NumberArray.
    BigIdTracker
    Tracker capable of keeping 6B range values, using ByteArray.
    EncodingIdMapper
    Maps arbitrary values to long ids.
    EncodingIdMapper.SameInputIdDetector  
    GroupCache.ByteGroupCache  
    GroupCache.ShortGroupCache  
    IntTracker
    Tracker capable of keeping int range values, using IntArray.
    LongCollisionValues
    Stores longs in a LongArray provided by NumberArrayFactory.
    LongEncoder
    Encoder that assumes that the entered strings can be parsed to Long directly.
    ParallelSort
    Sorts input data by dividing up into chunks and sort each chunk in parallel.
    Radix
    Calculates and keeps radix counts.
    Radix.Long  
    Radix.String  
    RadixCalculator
    Calculates the radix of RadixCalculator.Long values.
    RadixCalculator.Long
    Radix optimized for strings encoded into long by LongEncoder.
    RadixCalculator.String
    Radix optimized for strings encoded into long by StringEncoder.
    SameGroupDetector
    Used by EncodingIdMapper to help detect collisions of encoded values within the same group.
    StringCollisionValues
    Stores strings in a ByteArray provided by NumberArrayFactory.
    StringEncoder
    Encodes String into a long with very small chance of collision, i.e. two different Strings encoded into the same long value.
    TrackerFactories
    Common TrackerFactory implementations.
    Workers<R extends Runnable>
    Utility for running a handful of Runnable in parallel, each in its own thread.
